#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: es-football-bypass.php
msgid "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare"
msgstr "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: es-football-bypass.php
msgid "https://github.com/dcarrero/cf-football-bypass"
msgstr ""

#. Description of the plugin
#: es-football-bypass.php
msgid ""
"Operates with Cloudflare to toggle between Proxy (ON/CDN) and DNS Only (OFF) "
"based on IP blocks, with persistent DNS cache and AJAX actions. Separate UI: "
"Operation and Settings."
msgstr ""
"Opera amb Cloudflare per alternar Proxy (ON/CDN) i DNS Only (OFF) segons "
"bloquejos, amb memòria cau DNS persistent i accions AJAX. Interfície "
"separada: Operació i Configuració."

